translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ななな、何すんだよぉ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: W-What are you doing?!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「おいおいおいおい……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hey hey hey hey...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: これ、見てみろ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Look at this.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「『かおり14歳　乱れて、夏』」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Kaori, 14 years old — Disturbed, Summer"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「エロい奴！？　ねえ、これエロい奴！？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Is it something erotic?! Hey, is this something erotic?!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「いや、どうだろな……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Well, I wonder...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: タイトルだけじゃなんとも……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Just from the title, it's hard to say...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: だが、かなりそれっぽいよな？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: But it sure sounds like it, doesn't it?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「みみみ、見てみる？　見てみちゃう？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: W-W-Wanna take a look? Wanna take a peek?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 見よ見よ？　見てみよう？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Come on, come on? Let's take a look?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「駄目だ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: No.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「今、同じ部屋に乱義がいる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rangii is in the same room right now.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「え〜……いいじゃん、それくらい
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Eh~... That much is fine, isn't it?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ふざけろ、あいつの前で
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Don't be ridiculous, in front of him...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: エロラレラレ石なんぞ見られるか
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Would you show off your erotic 'Lalela' stone or whatever to him?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「だから、いいか？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: So listen, okay?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: まずロッキー辺りに言って、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: First, we'll talk to Rocky or someone,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あいつをなんとか退室させてだなぁ――
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: To get him to leave this room somehow—

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: （丸聞こえだ、馬鹿……）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: (You can hear all of that, idiot...)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＜コンコン＞
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: *Knock knock*
Hm?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: こんな時間に誰だろう……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Who could it be at this hour...?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「怪奇ラレラレ石見てたら
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: After watching the mysterious 'Lalela' stone,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 怖くなったので今日だけ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It scared me, so just for today,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 男部屋で一緒に寝かせて下さい
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Please let me sleep together in the men's room.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「く、下さい……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: P-Please...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「何してんだテメェら！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What the hell are you guys doing?!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「もー、一晩くらい、いいでしょー
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Come on, just for one night, isn't it okay?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「うう……ごめんね、ザンスちゃん……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ugh... I'm sorry, Zans-chan...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 本物の幽霊は平気なんだけど、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'm fine with real ghosts,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 作り物はちょっと駄目で……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: But fake ones are a bit too much for me...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「えへへ、こうやって皆同じ部屋で寝るなんて、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hehe, sleeping in the same room like this,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 小さかった頃を思い出すねー
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It reminds me of when we were little.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リセットはニコニコ笑顔で、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Reset smiled brightly,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いそいそと布団を敷いていた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and busily laid out the futons.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あっ、あれする？　あれする？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ah, wanna do that? Wanna do that?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 好きな人言いあいっこ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The game where we say who we like.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「おっ、それなら私、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Oh, then I'll

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 部屋からお菓子取ってこよっか
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: go get some snacks from the room.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「出てけや！！！！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Get out of here!!!!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「はあ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: *Sigh...*

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「というか、なんで私達まで……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I mean, why do we have to...?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 結局――
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: In the end—

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あなた達は仲良く同じ部屋で就寝した。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You all went to sleep together in the same room peacefully.
Month XX, Day XX—

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「雨がやまない……ですか？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The rain... won't stop, huh?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「はい、左様で
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Yes, that's correct.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 村長は忌々しげにカーテンの隙間から
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The village chief looked displeased through the gap in the curtains,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 曇天の空を仰ぎ見た。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and gazed up at the cloudy sky.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「この豪雨が降り出してから……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Since this heavy rain started falling...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: かれこれ一ヶ月になりますか
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It has been about a month, hasn't it?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「一ヶ月！？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A month?!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その間、ずっと降り続けてんすか！？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's been raining continuously all that time?!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「はい。その原因は……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Yes. The cause is...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: この近くにアーマーガエルが
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That an Armor Frog has made its nest nearby,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 巣を作ってしまったからなのです
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and that's why.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「旅人の皆さんにお願いするのは心苦しいのですが！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I feel bad asking travelers like you,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: どうか退治しては頂けないでしょうか！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: but could you please exterminate it!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: というわけで、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: And so,
